6 (i) As used in this section:
7 "Controlled group” means parent-subsidiary corporations,
8 brother-sister corporations, or constructive owner.
9 "Legal owner" includes a person who holds unencumbered
10 title to a vessel or is a secured party under a security
11 interest in the vessel.
12 "Owner" includes the legal owner of a vessel where there is
13 no security interest held by anyone on the vessel, a buyer under
14 a purchase money security interest, a debtor under any security
15 interest, a demise charterer of a vessel, or a lessee or
16 charterer of a vessel under a lease or charter which provides
17 the lessee or charterer with exclusive right to possession of
18 the vessel to the exclusion of the lessor or the person from
19 whom the vessel is chartered.
